**Reproduce code:**
```scala
object Test extends App{
  (new Child).mkInner(null)
}
class Child extends Parent{
  override def mkInner =
    c => {
      if(false) new Inner{}
  	  else super.mkInner(null)
    }
}
class Parent{
  def mkInner: Any => Inner = _ => new Inner
  class Inner
}
```

**Expected result:**
Compiles and runs fine

